### ========================================
### 财务/药品管理测试（新增 charge_item 流程）
### ========================================

### 31. 查询待收费项目
# 先挂号或开检查/检验/处置/处方，获取 registerId 后调用
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/finance/pending-items?registerId=6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 32. 查询已收费项目
# 收费成功后调用
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/finance/paid-items?registerId=6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 33. 收费（勾选部分项目）
# 从 pending-items 返回的 id 中选几个传入 itemIds
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/finance/charge
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "registerId": 6,
  "itemIds": [1, 2],
  "chargeMethod": "CASH",
  "amount": 325.00
}

### 34. 退费（勾选部分项目）
# 从 paid-items 返回的 id 中选几个传入 itemIds
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/finance/refund
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "registerId": 6,
  "itemIds": [1],
  "refundAmount": 300.00,
  "refundReason": "患者要求退费"
}

### 35. 收费记录查询
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/finance/records?pageNum=1&pageSize=10&startDate=2026-05-01&endDate=2026-06-30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 36. 日结统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/finance/daily-summary?summaryDate=2026-05-23
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 37. 药品库存查询
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/drug/inventory?pageNum=3&pageSize=10&stockAlert=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 38. 发药
# 处方状态需为 CHARGED
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/drug/dispense
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "prescriptionId": 1,
  "pharmacistId": 1
}

### 39. 退药
# 处方状态需为 DISPENSED
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/drug/refund
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "prescriptionId": 1,
  "pharmacistId": 1,
  "refundReason": "药品过敏"
}

